comment.author: 37426109@N07
comment._content:
I just noticed something quite unusual about the Number Plate on this Vehicle. It appears that the number plate is Black with white lettering, and the standard NSW at the top. What really stands out is, this vehicle has numbers only, no letters, whereas nowadays it's letters first then numbers (on plates which pre date the 3 double digit plates).

I wonder if the RTA (DMR) have any examples or archives they could post.?
